Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:10.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnTimes New Roman\fs18\c&H3B3F46&\3c&H8E908B&\shad0\b1}The Deep Blue Sea Is Everyone's Treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:12.20,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:16.22,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,We haven't even been away six months,\N but this is so nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:17.45,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I feel so relaxed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:23.08,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,But should we really be here? \NThe audition is tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:25.22,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is necessary, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.20,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:32.70,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Do you remember when you first said you \Nwanted to become a World Dai Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:35.24,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:38.59,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I think it was about when\NI graduated middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:40.88,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wrote it on my future plans survey at school
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:42.84,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,and my teacher looked so done with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:46.99,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, but I might've told\Nsomeone in class before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:50.53,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.34,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a World Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:55.90,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,That's what I want to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:03.13,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I told someone even before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:07.23,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Well, I figured you didn't remember, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:11.47,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what you're missing, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:12.16,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:19.23,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The great age of theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:24.76,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is the story of how to make\N one girl's dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:44.66,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,1)\fnArial\shad0\b1\frx-5\bord0\fs36\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(321.456,128.969)\t(\fs38)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:02.03,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(770,770)\fnTimes New Roman\an3\fs18\blur2\bord1\shad0\pos(604.933,308.933)\3c&H4B4B4C&}Our Promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:06.70,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,There was once a town\Nthat was the beating heart of theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:10.79,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,A town where actors and actresses \Nplayed all kinds of roles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.46,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,bringing countless stories to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:19.75,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,A certain young girl lived there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:24.36,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,She loved picture books and the \Nstories her parents would tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:30.85,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Eventually, she would become a storyteller\Ntoo and try various roles herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.08,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.83,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,That was when the girl first saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:40.93,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,a production put on by \Nactors called Dai Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:50.03,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,From that moment on,\Nshe was captivated by the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.62,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,She went to the theater over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.74,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,and reenacted the plays she saw there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:04:01.39,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Sometimes, she was a knight \Nwho swore fealty to the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:05.49,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Others, she was a young man madly in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.79,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,She'd get too into her role on occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.01,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,and cause trouble for the people around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.19,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Those were fun and happy days for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:20.12,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But they didn't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.19,Main,Shizuka (Young Kokona),0,0,0,,We're moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:26.97,Main,Shizuka (Young Kokona),0,0,0,,Our house will be smaller than it is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:30.28,Main,Shizuka (Young Kokona),0,0,0,,But why? What about theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:35.29,Main,Shizuka (Young Kokona),0,0,0,,I see... The ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.59,Main,Shizuka (Young Kokona),0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:45.31,Main,Shizuka (Young Kokona),0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll just go to see plays\N by saving up my allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:51.17,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,And so the girl arrived in a new town\Nwhere the sea and sky stretched out forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:55.72,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The scenery was unfamiliar,\Nand so were the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:59.02,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The theater was so far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.44,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,she had to take multiple trains to reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:06.61,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Her parents were busy and didn't \Ncome home until late into the evenings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:12.71,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,On top of that... she had trouble\Nmaking friends right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.98,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,She was bored to tears when she was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.95,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.65,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.75,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The little girl recalled the plays she'd seen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:09.45,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,and brought that dream world back to her, \None performance at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:16.48,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Day after day, she never tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:23.69,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But being by yourself is a lonely thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.68,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Then one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.67,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:43.34,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,We finally met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.03,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,Could you do that one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:53.96,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,You must like acting. I love it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:59.69,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Then let's do it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:05.39,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,The first friend I made after moving here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:10.47,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,She wasn't anyone from school, \Nand I could only meet her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:15.67,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,She loved acting, \Nknew all the plays I had seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.37,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,and was a better actor than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:23.49,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,We always wanted the same roles, \Nand you'd always let me have them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:28.25,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,just because you thought I'd play them better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:32.35,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,And my friend would always get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:37.26,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,She'd tell me I wouldn't be able to play \Na part well if I kept lying about how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.47,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:44.41,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,How did I forget all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.52,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Maybe it was because\Nyou couldn't control your Sense yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.82,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Not to mention that {\i1}this{\i0} was \Nthe stage we had to work with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:57.40,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Stage... my Sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.77,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm your Sense, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:11.72,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The partner you created because you \Nneeded someone to perform with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.64,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:24.81,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The receptacle for the feelings you couldn't\N sustain after you lost your confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:28.86,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,The feelings I couldn't sustain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.96,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I want to be on that stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:38.76,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I want the best role. \NI want to outshine everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.59,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Even if it means knocking other actors down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:48.60,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm totally better! \NMy performance was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.33,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I want to be onstage more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.49,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,So... why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.00,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Why doesn't anyone see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.49,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's not what I—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:00.59,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You {\i1}did{\i0} think it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.35,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I know your heart\Nbetter than anyone, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.62,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But it's okay to feel that way. You're an actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:15.23,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Especially if you want \Nto become a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.35,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Don't forget those feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:20.66,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:22.35,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:27.65,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm going to return these feelings to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:32.43,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I can't take the stage,\Nso I shouldn't hold on to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:37.63,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,No! I don't want them!\NYou keep them, Shizuka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:40.65,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I promise I'll play the roles \Nexactly how you tell me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:44.49,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You can't beat Kathrina and the \Nothers with half-hearted acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.88,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,But... I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.86,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,This is too sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:58.26,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Without you, Shizuka-chan, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.88,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I told you from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:04.70,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is the story of how you make\N your dream come true, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:08.67,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm not the star, so my role ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.56,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.17,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:25.65,Main - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I know you can make it happen, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:28.99,Main - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see your Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.05,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shizuka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,1)\fnArial\shad0\b1\frx-5\bord0\fs36\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(321.456,128.969)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:22.78,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:23.80,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:29.41,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Kathrin, how's your right eye doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.63,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,It's the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.25,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Kokona-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:40.00,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Are the four of you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.29,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kokona was supposed to go first,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:45.00,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,but if she's not here in time, \Nshe's not fit to play the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.79,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kathrina, I know you're not in your \Nbest condition, but are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.52,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.14,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Then come up to the stage—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.76,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:06.58,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Please let me, Kokona Otori, \Nplay the role of the Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.71,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You're always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:20.89,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kathrina, do you mind if Kokona goes first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:24.31,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,That's fine. I'm the one who's \Ngoing to win in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:28.57,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Kokona, you'll be docked \Npoints for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.06,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Do you still want to audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:33.05,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes! Please let me do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.62,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,I always have the same dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:05.17,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,I'm walking under the sun\Nwith nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:10.77,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,I can dine out like normal people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:13.35,Main - Italics,Panda,0,0,0,,This is the scene where \NChristine takes off his mask
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:14.89,Main - Top,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,I go to mass on Sundays and pray to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:16.01,Main - Italics,Panda,0,0,0,,and he becomes enraged but \Nalso tells her how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:19.03,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,No matter how unsightly I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:32.17,Main - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Being on a real stage was blinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:35.77,Main - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona's growth was blinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:41.09,Main - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I want to be up there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:47.86,Main - Italics,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll be able to stand on \Nthat stage overflowing with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.94,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,I still seek the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:56.66,Main - Italics,Niizuma,0,0,0,,There's no rage or resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.43,Main - Italics,Niizuma,0,0,0,,This is how the Phantom \Nfeels inside as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:02.43,Main - Italics,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Pure admiration for the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:05.10,Main - Italics,Kathrina,0,0,0,,To think she'd play the Phantom \Nwith that look on her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.91,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,I shall channel my rage into song!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.22,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,As my heart wills!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:27.03,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,So that I may forget my loneliness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:34.23,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,Music? It must be the opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.50,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,I cannot stand the sound of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:41.30,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,Let me play!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:44.18,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,I'll give you a true opera!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.79,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,It should be {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:50.62,Main - Italics,Niizuma,0,0,0,,That's the anger and loneliness \NShizuka-san portrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.58,Main - Top,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,No, that's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.61,Main - Top,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,I am but a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.51,Main,Kokona (Phantom),0,0,0,,A hideous monster.
