Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.91,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I totally lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.88,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.00,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:19.26,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I gave that performance my all.\N I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:22.42,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,The loneliness and rage of the Phantom \Nhiding deep within the opera house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:29.14,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I thought expressing that was the key to \Nshowing the Phantom's fear and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.50,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,The variations of the \NPhantom we tried to play
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:36.58,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,are probably extensions\Nof Hiiragi-san's Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:43.09,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'm sure that she saw new \Npotential in Kokona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:43.67,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an2\i1\shad0\bord0\fnTimes New Roman\c&H02040C&\frx354\fry334\frz354.2\move(524,214.667,535.667,210.334)}P\Nh\Na\Nn\Nt\No\Nm\N\No\Nf\N\Nt\Nh\Ne\N\NO\Np\Ne\Nr\Na{\i0}
