Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:49.74,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,His heart's weakness, its purity... \NThe longing to step outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:56.03,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,The annoyance, jealousy, and sadness\Nof being denied what he wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:16:00.08,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I'm surprised she played the role\N in such a complex way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.92,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.46,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It must be... Shizuka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.34,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Your Phantom was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.45,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shamo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:23.18,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,You don't look like an actor\Nwho just got the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.59,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Seems you haven't been able \Nto shake off the Phantom yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:31.54,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll ever be able \Nto shake him off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.36,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,That wasn't actually the Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:37.50,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,It was the Shizuka-chan who \Ndisappeared into my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.16,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:46.56,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Is this really how an actor who wants\Nto become a Dai Star should be looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:47.39,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:52.25,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Even after this production is done,\Nyour time on stage won't come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:58.75,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,I've watched many actors over \Nthe years. That's how I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:03.34,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,You still don't truly understand yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:09.35,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,To be on the stage\Nis to find yourself through acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:15.63,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Your Sense is born by facing the \Nbrilliance that lies dormant within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.10,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Find myself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.77,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Why don't we go downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.25,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.68,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.53,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:44.61,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,In front of you is your other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:47.44,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,The person you need to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:53.43,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Go on, ask her. Ask her what \Nyou want to do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:57.91,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,What I... want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:16.81,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Why did I want to become \Na World Dai Star again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:19.94,Main,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,You even forgot something that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:24.32,Main,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,It's because you love the theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.30,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,But that's not a rational thought to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:30.84,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,They're, like, the best of the absolute best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:34.51,Main,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Well, you fell in love with them.\NWhat can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:39.33,Main,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Besides, it's not just my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:40.47,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:46.64,Main,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,I would've lost hope if I'd been alone,\N so I needed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:52.11,Main,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Remember our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:04.13,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,It's no use. I've only ever \Nacted in front of my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.90,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,It's always easy to find reasons \N{\i1}not{\i0} to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.87,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,You know that, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:13.87,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,What's important is how you feel!\N How {\i1}you{\i0} feel, Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.79,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.62,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:22.22,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'll give you some advice. \NYou need to say your dreams out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.76,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,Say you're going to make them come true \Nand make yourself believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.52,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Make myself believe it? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.94,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.77,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,Just play the part of a girl with dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.29,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Play the part?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.22,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,Become her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:43.51,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,All so you can make your dream come \Ntrue and become a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.84,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,What about you, Shizuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:45.53,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:48.03,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,You're not going to be one, Shizuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.90,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,You're going to become one for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.22,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:02.61,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a World Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:03.67,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,That's what I want to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:07.30,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,If I can become one,\NI know {\i1}you'll{\i0} be one too, Shizuka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.78,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Then someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:14.22,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,Someday, let's take the stage together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.76,Flashback,Young Kokona,0,0,0,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.69,Flashback,Young Shizuka,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:35.65,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Someday, let's take the stage together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:44.82,Main,Shamo,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:49.14,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm going to go rehearse with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.88,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,so that I can see Shizuka-chan again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.57,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Koko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:06.51,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I have to work hard for Shizuka-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:12.19,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,I need to make {\i1}The Phantom of the Opera{\i0}\Na success so I can become a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.29,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:18.51,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Please help me out, everyone! \NI need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.38,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:33.40,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,You got nothing to worry about!\NWe're your friends, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.66,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,The only thing that should \Nbe dense is French baguettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:40.26,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,We'll rehearse with you lots!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:42.16,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.32,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:48.18,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You can have the role of the Phantom, \Nbut this time, I'm going to upstage you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.41,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You'd better be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.72,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:54.68,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,You're so young and edgy, Kathrin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.58,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,So edgy I might cut myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.41,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:21:59.61,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,That you're edgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:02.96,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,No, really! What does that even mean?!
